{"tid":825873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國向二千億美元中國商品加徵一成關稅　下周一生效","createTime":"2018-09-18T00:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T10:58:02.000Z","uid":141151,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"32412d63689f5e57ab715a79673944493900f692","tid":825873,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T00:29:24.000Z","msg":"美國向二千億美元中國商品加徵一成關稅　下周一生效<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1418635-20180918.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1418635-20180918.htm&d=in88Pmjn3G1wA9FuzEv35LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=b59ad4e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1418635-20180918.htm&h=f6e08012\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1418635-20180918.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰升級，美國總統特朗普宣布，對價值約2000億美元中國商品加徵10%關稅，下星期一起生效，預料到明年初，稅率將增加到25%。新關稅將適用於5000多種貨品，包括手袋、稻米和紡織品等。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在聲明中表示，中國的貿易政策對美國經濟構成嚴重威脅，警告如果北京採取報復行動，將立即進行第三階段徵稅，即對額外進口的約2670億美元貨品加徵關稅。特朗普在社交網站表示，提高關稅讓美國在貿易談判中佔上風，如果有國家不跟美國達成公平協議，他們將被關稅嚇怕。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中國政府早前已經表明，一旦美國進一步加徵關稅，將會採取報復性措施。</span><br />\n<br />\n亮劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c64ff72a1434a0215cb7d722c38a9f1a9957db2","tid":825873,"uid":60123,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T00:30:03.000Z","msg":"幾時先亮得呀 聽到悶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8103453970720f638dcf729d3f9c3172946d93d7","tid":825873,"uid":65292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T00:30:46.000Z","msg":"美國人民要受苦了<br />\n中國又贏"},{"pid":"f300fb34d5aec92066783819ade142dbe3e6d793","tid":825873,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T00:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces